.START 

American Express Co. named James A. Firestone to the new post of executive vice president of travel management services at the financial services, travel services and publishing company's American Express Travel Related Services Co. unit. 

Mr. Firestone, 35 years old, had been president and general manager of Travel Related Services/Japan. 

In addition, Brian P. Froelich, 43, was named executive vice president of travel for American Express Travel Related Services.
He will oversee the recently consolidated businesses of the Business & Retail Travel Network and Membership Travel Groups.
He had been senior vice president of business travel operations. 

